# Surge Rule-Set for Social Media (QQ Music & Xiaohongshu)
# 包含策略：REJECT-DROP, DIRECT, Proxy
# 建议引用方式：RULE-SET,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/YourUsername/RepoName/main/social_media_rules.list

# --- QQ Music P2P Block ---
# 阻断 QQ 音乐 P2P 节点与打洞服务器
DOMAIN,tp2p.kg.qq.com,REJECT-DROP
DOMAIN,twns.p2ptun.qq.com,REJECT-DROP
DOMAIN,musicps.p2p.qq.com,REJECT-DROP
DOMAIN,musicpunch.p2p.qq.com,REJECT-DROP

# --- Xiaohongshu Ads Block ---
# 拦截小红书商业化、广告与追踪相关域名
DOMAIN,ads-img-al.xhscdn.com,REJECT-DROP
DOMAIN,ads-img-qc.xhscdn.com,REJECT-DROP
DOMAIN,ads-video-al.xhscdn.com,REJECT-DROP
DOMAIN,ads-video-qc.xhscdn.com,REJECT-DROP
DOMAIN,ads-vp5.xhscdn.com,REJECT-DROP
DOMAIN-WILDCARD,ads-*.xhscdn.com,REJECT-DROP
DOMAIN,growth-img.xhscdn.com,REJECT-DROP
DOMAIN,sns-webpic.xhscdn.com,REJECT-DROP
DOMAIN,xhslive-video.xhscnd.com,REJECT-DROP

# --- Xiaohongshu Direct ---
# 直连放行小红书核心业务 API 与静态资源
DOMAIN,ci.xiaohongshu.com,DIRECT
DOMAIN,edith.xiaohongshu.com,DIRECT
DOMAIN,miniprogram.xiaohongshu.com,DIRECT
DOMAIN,pages.xiaohongshu.com,DIRECT
DOMAIN,picasso-static.xiaohongshu.com,DIRECT
DOMAIN,rec.xiaohongshu.com,DIRECT
DOMAIN,so.xiaohongshu.com,DIRECT
DOMAIN,live-room.xiaohongshu.com,DIRECT

# --- Xiaohongshu Proxy ---
# 网页端或特定入口路由至代理策略
DOMAIN,www.xiaohongshu.com,Proxy

# --- Xiaohongshu Fallback ---
# 兜底拦截未被放行的底层追踪与其他冗余请求
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,xiaohongshu.com,REJECT-DROP
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,redbascket.com,REJECT-DROP
